Agent brand logos
=================

This folder vendors the official brand marks shown next to each agent in the
Settings > Agents grid (see `ui/pages/settings/components/agent_logo.slint`).
One SVG per agent id. Documented here the same way `ui/assets/icons/LICENSE`
documents the vendored Lucide icons.

These are third-party brand/trademark assets, included solely to identify each
agent. They are NOT covered by this repository's own license; each remains the
property of its respective owner and is used nominatively (to name the product).
Refer to each owner's brand guidelines before reproducing these marks elsewhere.


claude-code.svg  --  "Claude"  (Anthropic)
  Source : Simple Icons  https://cdn.simpleicons.org/claude
  Upstream: https://github.com/simple-icons/simple-icons  (icon slug: claude)
  License: Simple Icons artwork is released under CC0 1.0 (public domain). The
           mark itself is a trademark of Anthropic PBC.
  Native brand color baked into the SVG (fill #D97757). Rendered un-colorized.

gemini-cli.svg  --  "Google Gemini"  (Google)
  Source : Simple Icons  https://cdn.simpleicons.org/googlegemini
  Upstream: https://github.com/simple-icons/simple-icons  (icon slug: googlegemini)
  License: Simple Icons artwork is CC0 1.0 (public domain). The mark is a
           trademark of Google LLC.
  Native brand color baked into the SVG (fill #8E75B2). Rendered un-colorized.

codex.svg  --  OpenAI mark, standing in for "Codex"  (OpenAI)
  Source : openai/codex (the Codex CLI's own repository -- first-party)
           https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openai/codex/main/codex-rs/skills/src/assets/samples/openai-docs/assets/openai-small.svg
  SUBSTITUTION: there is no distinct "Codex" brand mark. Simple Icons no longer
           carries an OpenAI icon (removed upstream). This is OpenAI's own
           logomark, taken directly from the Codex product repository, used as
           the closest official mark for the `codex` agent.
  License: subject to OpenAI's brand/trademark terms. Monochrome SVG
           (fill="currentColor"); rendered colorized to the theme text color.

amp.svg  --  "Amp"  (Sourcegraph)
  Source : ampcode.com (Amp's own site -- first-party)  https://ampcode.com/amp-mark.svg
  NOTE   : Simple Icons' "amp" slug is Google AMP (Accelerated Mobile Pages), a
           different product, so it was NOT used. This is the real Sourcegraph
           Amp mark pulled from the product's own domain.
  License: subject to Sourcegraph's brand/trademark terms. The mark ships as a
           monochrome white glyph (fill="white"); rendered colorized to the
           theme text color so it is visible on both light and dark surfaces.
